lead_paragraph: Across the East Texas triangle that connects Austin, College Station and Houston, most everybody is happy with their favorite team's college football coach after the first weekend of the season.

headline.print_headline: In Opening Weekend, Texas Coaching Triangle Keeps Fans Happy
